items.title: nodejs/node v25.7.0
items.key_takeaway: Node.js v25.7.0 (minor release) adds http2 http1 fallback options, ESM entry point support in SEA, a sqlite release candidate, and renames a stream API option, offering new backend capabilities and minor API changes.

items.title: nodejs/node v24.14.0
items.key_takeaway: Node.js v24.14.0 LTS adds several minor but useful features such as async_hooks trackPromises, an ignore option for fs.watch, http.setGlobalProxyFromEnv, subpath import support, and other API tweaks, enhancing observability and configurability for backend services.
